593
00:29:21,841 --> 00:29:23,321
This is a treasure
from the Western Region.

594
00:29:23,321 --> 00:29:24,160
Treasure?

595
00:29:24,680 --> 00:29:25,321
This is very valuable.

596
00:29:25,841 --> 00:29:26,321
Let me see it.

597
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:26,801
No.

598
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:27,880
