to the divine servants.

632
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:37,480
They'll give it to the commoners nearby.

633
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:39,440
Miss Xuelu,

634
00:30:39,601 --> 00:30:41,121
you know General Qing very well.

635
00:30:44,041 --> 00:30:45,240
