649
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:07,160
Yan.

650
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:10,720
The Crimson King is in his 40s.

651
00:32:11,041 --> 00:32:12,440
He's not as powerful as before.

652
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,761
