735
00:37:12,200 --> 00:37:14,280
The second round is a wisdom test.

736
00:37:14,921 --> 00:37:17,081
To choose the first disciple.

737
00:37:21,081 --> 00:37:22,160
This is my artifact.

738
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:25,481
