790
00:40:38,720 --> 00:40:39,521
Look at the fuss he makes

791
00:40:39,680 --> 00:40:41,200
in the selection of his disciple.

792
00:40:42,081 --> 00:40:43,240
Back then,

793
00:40:43,720 --> 00:40:44,521
